nhc_headline: ...HURRICANE WARNING ISSUED FOR THE AZORES... ...GABRIELLE CONTINUES MOVING QUICKLY EAST-NORTHEASTWARD ACROSS THE NORTH ATLANTIC...
summary: ...HURRICANE WARNING ISSUED FOR THE AZORES... ...GABRIELLE CONTINUES MOVING QUICKLY EAST-NORTHEASTWARD ACROSS THE NORTH ATLANTIC... As of 5:00 AM AST Wed Sep 24 the center of Gabrielle was located near 35.6, -51.5 with movement ENE at 25 mph. The minimum central pressure was 959 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 115 mph.
